 na, evo,

310
00:17:40,020 --> 00:17:41,900
 malo da protresete svoje savjesti

311
00:17:41,900 --> 00:17:43,540
 i da pred gospodinom

312
00:17:43,540 --> 00:17:44,960
 kad vam sad tu bude izložen,

313
00:17:44,960 --> 00:17:47,360
 zaista sami sebi postavite pitanje

314
00:17:47,360 --> 00:17:48,720
 jesmo li mi sposobni

315
00:17:48,720 --> 00:17:49,480
 za nešto više?

316
00:17:51,100 --> 00:17:52,760
 Jesam li ja sposobna obećati

