00:17:52,760 --> 00:17:54,740
 da to neće biti tako?

318
00:17:54,740 --> 00:17:56,240
 Da sve ja mogu mijeniti se?

319
00:17:56,240 --> 00:17:58,340
 To su stvari koje mi sebi

320
00:17:58,340 --> 00:17:59,400
 moramo postaviti.

321
00:17:59,400 --> 00:17:59,820
 Pazite,

322
00:17:59,820 --> 00:18:01,300
 i moramo se naravno boriti.

323
00:18:01,300 --> 00:18:03,280
 Čistoća vam je

324
00:18:03,280 --> 00:18:04,280
