00:18:18,940 --> 00:18:19,520
 čovječija

336
00:18:19,520 --> 00:18:20,580
 postaje sebično.

337
00:18:20,580 --> 00:18:21,420
 Odnosno,

338
00:18:21,420 --> 00:18:22,060
