00:18:32,460 --> 00:18:33,380
 ostaćete prazni.

348
00:18:33,380 --> 00:18:34,740
 Obično ljudi

349
00:18:34,740 --> 00:18:35,420
 iz takvih veza

350
00:18:35,420 --> 00:18:36,480
