00:18:50,540 --> 00:18:51,500
 Ja sam ih isto imala

363
00:18:51,500 --> 00:18:52,500
 priliku slušati

364
00:18:52,500 --> 00:18:54,680
 da je to moguće.

365
00:18:54,680 --> 00:18:56,900
 I to je doista moguće.

