00:19:01,380 --> 00:19:03,620
 Nisam.

372
00:19:04,620 --> 00:19:05,440
 prije ne bi sam došla

373
00:19:05,440 --> 00:19:06,020
 od samostani,

374
00:19:06,020 --> 00:19:06,500
 ja sam imala

375
00:19:06,500 --> 00:19:07,380
 isto tako dečka.

376
00:19:07,380 --> 00:19:08,200
 Četiri godine.

377
00:19:08,200 --> 00:19:10,960
 I živjela sam tu

378
00:19:10,960 --> 00:19:12,160
 predbračnu čistoću.

379
00:19:12,160 --> 00:19:13,740
 Naravno,

380
00:19:13,740 --> 00:19:14,920
 kad me pukao poziv,

381
00:19:14,920 --> 00:19:15,800
 to je bilo

382
00:19:15,800 --> 00:19:16,320
 jako teško

383
00:19:16,320 --> 00:19:17,400
 prihvatati toj osobi.

384
00:19:17,400 --> 00:19:19,260
 Čak je bilo

385
00:19:19,260 --> 00:19:20,320
 dolazak od samostan

386
00:19:20,320 --> 00:19:20,740
 po mene

387
00:19:20,740 --> 00:19:21,640
 i tako dalje.

388
00:19:21,640 --> 00:19:23,240
 Svega se to odvijalo,

389
00:19:23,240 --> 00:19:23,980
 jer ja nisam baš

390
00:19:23,980 --> 00:19:24,680
 odišla odmah

391
00:19:24,680 --> 00:19:24,980
 onako.

