00:19:37,960 --> 00:19:38,820
 i ne mogu ne da nisam

406
00:19:38,820 --> 00:19:39,340
 bila spravna

407
00:19:39,340 --> 00:19:40,640
 čak i na brak s njima.

408
00:19:40,640 --> 00:19:42,600
 Ali javio se poziv.

409
00:19:42,600 --> 00:19:43,760
 Ja sam se uvijek

410
00:19:43,760 --> 00:19:44,620
 u sebi borila.

411
00:19:44,620 --> 00:19:46,800
 Ja to želim,

412
00:19:46,800 --> 00:19:47,500
 ja to želim.

413
00:19:47,500 --> 00:19:48,700
 Ja sam tom čovjeku

414
00:19:48,700 --> 00:19:49,520
 to priznala.

415
00:19:49,520 --> 00:19:51,400
 I on je pod uvijecu,

416
00:19:51,400 --> 00:19:52,660
 tešto da ja osjećam

417
00:19:52,660 --> 00:19:53,340
 u sebi poziv,

418
00:19:53,340 --> 00:19:53,700
 on je rekla

419
00:19:53,700 --> 00:19:54,700
 ja želim im biti stokom.

420
00:19:54,700 --> 00:19:56,440
 I bili smo

