00:19:56,440 --> 00:19:57,440
 u vezi četiri godine

422
00:19:57,440 --> 00:19:57,960
 nakon toga

423
00:19:57,960 --> 00:19:59,120
 ja odlazim u samostan.

424
00:19:59,840 --> 00:20:01,080
 Ja sam bila presretna

425
00:20:01,080 --> 00:20:02,220
 jer sam uspjela

